課程概述 Course Description
       無機化學之簡介、原子的結構、簡單的鍵結理論、對稱與群論、分子軌域、酸鹼化學、晶狀固態物質的結構與性質、及主族元素的化學。 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    To learn Atomic Structures, Bonding Theories, Symmetry and Group Theory, Molecular Orbitals, Acid-Base and Donor-Acceptor Interactions, Coordination Chemistry, Organometallic Chemistry, and Homogeneous Catalysis.    

